quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Naizvozvo vatumwa (ngirozi) pavakauya kune mhuri yaLut (Loti)
  15,62,"(Loti) Akati: “Zvirokwazvo, muri vanhu vasingazivikanwi kwandiri.”"
  15,63,"(Ngirozi) Dzikati: “Asi tauya kwauri neizvo zvavaisatenda mazviri.”"
  15,64,"“Uye taunza chokwadi kwauri (nyaya yekuparadzwa kwevanhu vako), uye zvirokwazvo, tinotaura chokwadi.”"
  15,65,"“Saka chiva unofamba muchidimbu cheusiku nemhuri yako, uye iwe wotevera kumashure kwavo, uye pakati penyu ngapasave nemunhu anocheuka kumashure, asi endai kwamakakomekedzwa.”"
  15,66,"Uye takaita basa iri kuti rizivikamwe kwaari, kuti midzi yeavo (vatadzi) ichave inodamburwa mangwanani ngwanani"
  15,67,Uye vagari vemudhorobha vakauya vachifara (nenyaya yemajaya ange auya aya)
  15,68,"(Loti) Akati: “Zvirokwazvo, ava vaenzi vangu, saka musandinyadzisewo.”"
  15,69,“Uye ityai Allah uye musave munondinyadzisa.”
  15,70,"(Vagari vemudhorobha) vakati: “Hatina kukurambidza here kutambira (kana kudzivirira) vanhu?”"
  15,71,"(Loti) akati: “Ava vanasikana vangu (kana muchida kuroora zviri pamutemo), kana muchikwanisa kudaro.”"
  15,72,"Zvirokwazvo, ndinopika nehupenyu hwako (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo varimukudhakwa vaingofamba"
  15,73,Naizvozvo vakava vanoparadzwa neAs-Swaaihah (Ruzha) panguva dzemangwanani
  15,74,"Uye takapindurudza (Sodom kuPalestine) tikaita kuti pamusoro paende pasi, uye tikave tinonaisa matombo akaumbwa nedhaka"
  15,75,"Zvirokwazvo, mukati meizvi mune micherechedzo kune avo vanoona"
  15,76,"Uye zvirokwazvo, maguta maviri aya akanga ari munzira hombe (kubva kuMakkah kuenda kuSyria, pane gungwa reDead Sea iyezvino)"
  15,77,"Zvokwadi, zvirokwazvo mune izvi mune mucherechedzo kune avo vanotenda"
  15,78,Uye vagari vemusango (vekuMadyan (Midian)) avo vakatumirwa Muporofita Shuaib (AS)) vakanga vari vanhu vaiita zvakaipa
  15,79,Naizvozvo takatsiva nemutongo wakaomarara kwavari. Ari maviri ari munzira hombe iri pachena